snippet.title: MARROW Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
MARROW is a fan made, original episode for Blood. 
Continuing Caleb's story after the defeat of Tchernobog, Caleb returns to the grave to rest. Yet, the Cabal have other plans. In an effort to resurrect Cerberus and destroy Caleb once and for all. Caleb must, once again, rise from the dead to defeat the remnants of the Cabal. 

With ten brand new levels, and featuring new, original music. 
MARROW is made for Blood: Fresh Supply, but will work with nBlood and Raze. (though may have graphical glitches not present in Fresh Supply)

https://playmarrow.com/

https://www.moddb.com/mods/marrow
